<sentence type="quasi">●生育に適した環境</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　日当たりと水はけがよい環境。</sentence>
<sentence>低温と乾燥に弱く、寒地では室内で冬越しさせる。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">●殖やし方（４〜５月中旬）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　種子まきで殖やす。</sentence>
<sentence>発芽適温が２０℃以上なので、４月以降に水はけのよい場所にまく。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">●苗の植えつけ（４月中旬〜７月）</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　十分暖かくなってから行う。</sentence>
<sentence>３０ｃｍ以上の深さに耕し、腐葉土を多めにすき込む。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">●病害虫</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　丈夫で、育てやすく、病害虫の心配はほとんど必要ない。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
<titleBlock>
<title>
<sentence type="quasi">●肥料</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　３〜４月、１０月に固形肥料を置肥する。</sentence>
<sentence>窒素肥料は控えめに。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
