<br type="automatic_original" />
</title>
</titleBlock>
<paragraph>
<sentence>　乾燥に弱いので、地植えでも時々水やりを。</sentence>
<sentence>鉢植えは表土が乾いたらたっぷり施す。</sentence>
<br type="automatic_original" />
</paragraph>
